Idea is to count characters using 5 variables. As in the "balloon"  char 'l' and 'o'
occours 2 times so at the end we will divide the total occourence of 'l' and 'o' with 2.
```
```
int maxNumberOfBalloons(string text) {

        int b=0, a=0, l2=0, o2=0, n=0;

        for(int i=0;i<text.size();i++){

            if(text[i]=='b') b++;
            else if(text[i]=='a') a++;
            else if(text[i]=='l') l2++;
            else if(text[i]=='o') o2++;
            else if(text[i]=='n') n++;
        }
        l2=l2/2;  o2=o2/2;  //both occours 2 times in the balloon
        int ans=min({b, a, l2, o2, n}); // min occourence of the char would be the solution
        return ans;
    }
```

